      "标题": "PlanRAG: A Plan-then-Retrieval Augmented Generation for Generative Large Language Models as Decision Makers",
      "作者": ["Myeonghwa Lee", "Seonho An", "Min-Soo Kim"],
      "发表时间": "2024-06-18",
