      "关键词": ["Decision QA", "retrieval-augmented generation", "plan-then-retrieval", "multi-hop reasoning"],
      "摘要": "We define Decision QA as the task of answering the best decision, d_best, for a decision-making question Q, business rules R and a database D. We propose Decision QA benchmark, DQA, with two scenarios, Locating and Building, constructed from two video games that have almost the same goal as Decision QA. To address Decision QA effectively, we also propose a new RAG technique called the iterative plan-then-retrieval augmented generation (PlanRAG). Our PlanRAG-based LM generates the plan for decision making as the first step, and the retriever generates the queries for data analysis as the second step. The proposed method outperforms the state-of-the-art iterative RAG method by 15.8% in the Locating scenario and by 7.4% in the Building scenario, respectively.",
